name: VOICE_CONVERSION_PRESET
description:
The options for SDK preset voice conversion effects.Since
                    v3.3.1

parameters.VOICE_CONVERSION_OFF: Turn off voice conversion effects and use the original voice.

parameters.VOICE_CHANGER_NEUTRAL: A gender-neutral voice. To avoid audio distortion, ensure that you use this enumerator to process a female-sounding voice.

parameters.VOICE_CHANGER_SWEET: A sweet voice. To avoid audio distortion, ensure that you use this enumerator to process a female-sounding voice.

parameters.VOICE_CHANGER_SOLID: A steady voice. To avoid audio distortion, ensure that you use this enumerator to process a male-sounding voice.

parameters.VOICE_CHANGER_BASS: A deep voice. To avoid audio distortion, ensure that you use this enumerator to process a male-sounding voice.
